results.name: Irregular triangle C(n,g) counting the connected 8-regular simple graphs on n vertices with girth at least g.
comment: The first column is for girth at least 3. The row length is incremented to g-2 when n reaches A054760(8,g).
link: Jason Kimberley, Index of sequences counting connected k-regular simple graphs with girth at least g
xref: Connected 8-regular simple graphs with girth at least g: this sequence (triangle); chosen g: A014378 (g=3), A181154 (g=4).
Connected 8-regular simple graphs with girth exactly g: A184980 (triangle); chosen g: A184983 (g=3).

Triangular arrays C(n,g) counting connected simple k-regular graphs on n vertices with girth at least g: A185131 (k=3), A184941 (k=4), A184951 (k=5), A184961 (k=6), A184971 (k=7), this sequence (k=8), A184991 (k=9).
